Title: Barnstormers
Plot: Vic and Emma try to help a woman who's in an abusive relationship. Vic and the Strike Team begin to make plans for the money train take down, even though the greenlight still has them on their toes. When David tells Dutch that he embarrassed the department with the Bob and Marcy case and that Claudette is now lead on all their cases, he's forced to take any action necessary to prove himself in a new homicide.  Danny finally makes a stand against Yassirah.
GuestStars: David Rees Snell, Cathy Cahlin Ryan, Monnae Michaell, Jason Padgett, Marcos De La Cruz, Marguerite MacIntyre, Melanie Lynskey, Karen Malina White, Mike Bruner, Keith Diamond, Nichole Hiltz
